// ============================================================
// inject_rtti_err_bad_arg_type.lox — Array arg to Delphi method
// ============================================================
// Setup: Delphi injects a TCustomer as global 'cust'.
//
// What this tests:
//   - Passing a Lox array where a Delphi string parameter is expected
//   - Overload selection scores the array as incompatible with the string
//     parameter, so no overload matches and a runtime error is raised
print cust.Name; // expect: Alice
var arr = [1, 2, 3];
cust.SetInfo(arr, 10); // expect runtime error: No overload of 'SetInfo' matches the given 2 argument(s).
